<section>
    <h2 class="highlight">Juke Joint ChatBot</h2>
    <p>
        A conversational GPT-based chatbot designed to emulate a personable assistant for small business owners.  
        Built in <strong>Python</strong> and <strong>Gradio</strong>, hosted on <strong>Hugging Face Spaces</strong>.  
        Incorporates humor, efficiency, and financial analysis capabilities.
    </p>
