<section>
    <h2 class="highlight">Blueprint Automation</h2>
    <p>
        Automation framework at Amazon that accelerates refund validation and contra-COGS cleanup.  
        Integrated <strong>UiPath</strong> with <strong>internal AR/AP datasets</strong> and improved throughput 40%.
    </p>
</section>

<section>
    <h2 class="highlight">Collect Dashboard</h2>
    <p>
        A <strong>Power Query + DAX</strong> dashboard that consolidates open invoice data across regions, providing
        daily insight into collection risk and opportunities for automation.  
        Designed to be simple, dynamic, and CFO-ready.
    </p>
</section>

<section>
    <h2 class="highlight">TariffGPT</h2>
    <p>
        A specialized GPT assistant that explains import tariffs and government efficiency program (DOGE) policies in plain English.  
        Uses <strong>OpenAI API</strong> for natural-language Q&A and <strong>Python Flask</strong> for API routing.
    </p>
</section>

<section>
    <h2 class="highlight">DOGE Automation Initiative</h2>
    <p>
        Department of Government Efficiency (DOGE) project streamlining holdback reconciliations with robotic process automation.  
        Improved accuracy while cutting manual review hours by 70%.
    </p>
</section>

